{"type": "article", "id": 30966, "title": "现金越来越少用，钱包也该越来越简单丨这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-08-12T23:25:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 31459, "name": "钱包设计"}, {"id": 31460, "name": "Dfywallets"}, {"id": 31461, "name": "PARSEC Design Studio"}, {"id": 31462, "name": "Bellroy"}, {"id": 31463, "name": "Tanner Goods"}, {"id": 31464, "name": "Horween"}, {"id": 31465, "name": "Tove Emilsson"}, {"id": 31466, "name": "CHIEH TING HUANG"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 494, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160813010554WG5JmUoIfnBHeLj7.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><p>          </p><p>当手机可以完成支付功能之后，零钱似乎就不用带在身上了，传统的钱包的功能在降低。在极简设计的大潮中，钱包也追求极简，没有太多的装饰或样式，留给“钱”的空间也并不多，也许这就是年轻一代对待生活的态度吧。</p><h3>Hunters Bend by Tove Emilsson</h3><p class=\"\">伦敦的设计师 Tove Emilsson 设计的这组钱包都只使用了一张皮，折叠后放在沸水中硬化，就形成了现在充满折纸感的样子。这种方式是设计师的特有的“工艺”，也让钱包的形态跳出传统的样子，更具有手工感。颜色上她选择了接近木头颜色的裸色，配上蓝色的拉链边或标签牌，也增加了一些新鲜感。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608130106375RiL6wN9rV8mJ7OC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.835470\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813010637XQy42mCd0sFe1nkD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813010637nX83ka2CpDlcHZ6w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813010638woM5ZFId71qDHNaR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813010729Ge1Hw30ADZUm9KQy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MINIMALIST WALLET SOLUTION by CHIEH TING HUANG</h3><p>这套极简皮质钱包同样只使用了一块皮，而没有使用针线，仅仅用弹簧圈将皮具封口。三角形的钱包专门放银币，其中一个角可以插入和拿出，就像是一个口袋的开口。方形的钱包放对折后的零钱或卡，弹簧圈也就有固定的作用。这套钱包呈现出一种简洁的几何感，容易让人眼前一亮。设计师来自台湾，在英国创立了工作室。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813011034JOCSG5I0ANPT3BVM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.836000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813011034jl5rONvxZLTP43gW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813011034EdDkMclBHF4en6QZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813011034weklUgfmGHoKxYDc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813011036prZbt5u8Dn2xhGKR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813011039BDtriNHjufdE61aG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>DFY by Dfywallets</h3><p class=\"\">DFY 是一个月前刚刚放在众筹网 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/dfywallets/dfy-rfid-minimalist-wallets-with-no-ridiculous-mar?ref=popular\" rel=\"nofollow\">kickstarter </a>上的一款钱包，目前已达到预期的 718%。它在设计上极力追求极简和最小，没有任何的花纹一类的装饰，是最简单的方形。材料上采用超细纤维皮革（microfiber leather），厚度只有 6 毫米，可以插入身份证、三张卡和一些零钱等。这样的钱包很符合现代生活的需要，在有了手机支付之后，钱包的功能也相应简化了。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813011644mR5FZDebEU6IPGKs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813011631FADx59zw1QamOLoS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016081301164792SN0u5bK4hxsTke.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.327941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813011631n02rH97W4fOeuLFJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813011631B0niGySbw1foClDg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Treether by PARSEC Design Studio</h3><p>融合了木头与皮革两种材料的设计可不只有硬邦邦的家具，台湾工作室 PARSEC 推出的 <a href=\"http://www.parsec-ds.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Treether</a> 木制钱包会让你在惊叹之余重新认识到木材的美，跳脱出木制品的传统框架。Treether 由工作室研发的“树革”制成，设计总监徐秒在薄木片和植鞣皮革之间加入了人造纤维制成的支撑网，最终克服了木料断裂这一难题。由于每一块木头各不相同，成品的纹理都是独一无二的，摸上去还能感受到温润的手感。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/parsec-ds/treether-wallets-made-with-premium-and-rare-wood\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，短夹的早鸟价为 99 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013902TiotkepEM90dIhFc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562135\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608130138578wvHeVU5d4M6ahqb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013901suaN9f31lpLgxOk2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013857VWx69G03JkXmK1Aj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013859yC5w4091ZOsABMPv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013859DmJlCkgvQxeIhWuZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Note Sleeve by Bellroy</h3><p>来自澳大利亚的 Andy Fallshaw 和 Hadrien Monloup 早在学生时代就希望能够打造出更完美的钱包，2010 年他们抱着“让钱包更轻”（slim your wallet）这一理念在墨尔本创立了 Bellroy。日常系列中能够容纳 4 到 11 张卡片的 Note Sleeve 就是一款平衡了尺寸和容量的设计，多个卡位可以通过拉扣叠放在一起以保持轻薄的外形，不会让口袋显得臃肿。大钞夹中有一个隐蔽的硬币袋，还能起到保护名片的作用。这是它的<a href=\"http://bellroy.com/products/note-sleeve-wallet/leather/black\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 89.95 澳元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013923is0yvAKxD7ZbQz61.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730769\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013922O1ScJLTExPt9NilK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013923Oxhl7ipYydeWMmND.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.520848\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013923Rs2OYdgM46HrxtLN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.520848\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013924yOt7EzxdXWmPHAZU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.520848\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013924IYsyamg4hQxctqHn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Universal Zip Wallet by Tanner Goods</h3><p>和其他美国手工皮具品牌一样，诞生于波特兰的 Tanner Goods 一直以来都坚持着传统工艺，所使用的皮革则来自芝加哥著名的 Horween 工厂。在最近推出的限量版 Universal Zip 系列中，设计师们在表面添加了装饰性的冲孔，为它增添了一股现代感。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.tannergoods.com/search?type=product&amp;q=universal\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 130 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013944dVcslLHMpPRwKef1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013946TNawOrdkfgYxpU3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013946mU05Krx1TfZQP2Js.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013947h4qZ6mCJN23eI9iQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160813013947s36bqCtDuwcG7z4A.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608130139482NVsy5nIkDilFf0t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}